roughcut.media.videoeditor

Interface VideoEditor.PreviewProgressListener

  • Enclosing interface:
    VideoEditor

    public static interface VideoEditor.PreviewProgressListener
    This listener interface is used by the VideoEditor to emit preview progress notifications. This callback should be invoked after the number of frames specified by #startPreview(android.view.SurfaceHolder surfaceHolder, long fromMs, long toMs, boolean loop, int callbackAfterFrameCount, roughcut.media.videoeditor.VideoEditor.PreviewProgressListener listener)
